docs {
  Runs the agent pipeline (retrieval -> research -> gap -> tool_agent -> solution)
  and PAUSES before the roadmap (interrupt_before). Returns gaps awaiting approval.
  Needs ANTHROPIC_API_KEY; takes ~30s. Then review in /admin/approvals or via the
  Pending/State/Approve requests below.
}
